admanager-desc: Ad d-imudd [[Special:AdManager|page spéciale]] ara yessirgen i sysops ad srsen tamnaḍt deg iwen n umḍiq i yisebtar neɣ taggayin
admanager_docu: Akken ad ternuḍ neq ad tekkseḍ tamnaḍt n usebter neɣ taggayt i meṛṛa, rnu neɣ kkes azwel n usebter neɣ taggayt ddaw-a.
admanagerzones_docu: Sekcem yal uṭṭun n temnaḍt n udellel ɣef izirig-is.
admanager_invalidtargetpage: Ulac ula d yiwen n usebter yettwafen s uzwel "$1".
admanager_notable: Tuccḍa! Tafelwit n taffa n isefka yettwasran ur tettwaf ara! Senker di tazwara update.php.
admanager_noAdManagerZones: Tuccḍa! Yessefk ad ternuḍ timnaḍin n udellel. Sekcem di [[Special:AdManagerZones|timnadin n umsefrak n udellel]].
